import { Icon } from "@iconify/react";
import { Button, Container, Stack, Typography } from "@mui/material";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import {
  Box,
  Card,
  Chip,
  Divider,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemDecorator,
} from "@mui/joy";

export default function ExperienceTimelinePart() {
  return (
    <Container
      maxWidth="fluid"
      sx={{ backgroundColor: "#0D0D0D", pt: 15, pb: 15 }}
    >
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Stack
          direction="row"
          alignItems="center"
          justifyContent="center"
          mb={5}
        >
          <Typography
            variant="h4"
            gutterBottom
            color="white"
            textAlign="center"
            sx={{
              background:
                "linear-gradient(primary,primary) left 0 bottom 10% /100% 20% no-repeat",
            }}
          >
            Experience
          </Typography>
        </Stack>
        <Box
          sx={{
            width: "100%",
            display: "grid",
            gridTemplateColumns:
              "repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(100%, 300px), 1fr))",
            gap: 2,
          }}
        >
          <Card
            size="lg"
            variant="outlined"
            sx={{ backgroundColor: "transparent" }}
          >
            <Chip size="sm" variant="outlined" color="neutral">
              Istanbul 
            </Chip>
            <Typography level="h2" sx={{ color: "white" }}>
              Professional
            </Typography>
            <Divider inset="none" />
            <List size="sm" sx={{ mx: "calc(-1 * var(--ListItem-paddingX))" }}>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Virtual Credit Cards
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Financial Analytics
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Checking Account
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                API Integration
              </ListItem>
            </List>
          </Card>
          <Card
            size="lg"
            variant="outlined"
            sx={{ backgroundColor: "transparent" }}
          >
            <Chip size="sm" variant="outlined" color="neutral">
              BASIC
            </Chip>
            <Typography level="h2" sx={{ color: "white" }}>
              Professional
            </Typography>
            <Divider inset="none" />
            <List size="sm" sx={{ mx: "calc(-1 * var(--ListItem-paddingX))" }}>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Virtual Credit Cards
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Financial Analytics
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Checking Account
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                API Integration
              </ListItem>
            </List>
          </Card>
        </Box>
        <Stack justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" width="100%" mt={10}>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            size="large"
            component={Link}
            to={"../experience"}
            sx={{
              backgroundColor: "primary",
              color: "black",
              textTransform: "capitalize",
              borderRadius: 2,
              width: 150,
            }}
          >
            See More
          </Button>
        </Stack>
      </Container>
    </Container>
  );
}
